{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778904516253,"sessionID":"ses_1d10b32d6ffeB5EC7XHcXmN86q","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"functions.write:32","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"Following up on this issue, I have committed the fix for the incorrect `part_of` relationship on `UBERON:0006678` (`foramen secundum`).\n\n**Summary of the change:**\n- The definition was corrected from \"A foramen in the septum secundum.\" to \"A foramen in the septum primum.\", which is consistent with the existing `external_definition` field and with anatomical literature (Wikipedia article, medical anatomy textbook ISBN:9632412311).\n- The logical definition was updated from `part_of some 'atrial septum secundum'` (`UBERON:0004155`) to `part_of some 'atrial septum primum'` (`UBERON:0004154`).\n\nThe change is now reflected in the edit file. If the NCIT direction is also incorrect as discussed, a separate request to NCIT would be needed since it is an external ontology.\n\n@rays22, please feel free to review the correction.\n\nFixes #3522.\n","filePath":"/home/runner/work/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/runner/work/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"ISSUE_COMMENTS.md","time":{"start":1778904516241,"end":1778904516251}},"id":"prt_e2ef8b061001KmNdZIZevSV9Zp","sessionID":"ses_1d10b32d6ffeB5EC7XHcXmN86q","messageID":"msg_e2ef8a6bd001v0vY0p6A7jfybR"}}
